Dynamic Ten-Zone RGB Lighting: Illuminate your system with ten individually addressable, ultra-bright RGB LEDs per module,

Create and Customize: Choose from dozens of preset lighting profiles, or create your own in iCUE.

and frequency readings, onboard voltage regulation, and custom XMP profiles.
